<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-KK94CHFLLe+nY2dmCWGMq91rCGa5gtU4mk92HdvYe+M/SXH301p5ILy+dN9+nJOZ" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geologica:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
    <title>UpperWorker</title>
</head>
<body class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">
    <div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 mx-auto flex-column">
        <header class="justify-content-around mx-4 mt-4 px-2">
            <div class="">
                <nav class="nav justify-content-between">
                    <h3 class="">UpperWorker</h3>
                    <ul class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="#">Home</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/areas">Areas</a>
                    <% if(!currentUser){ %>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                    <% } %>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>
        <main class="px-3 mb-auto mt-auto">
            <h1>UpperWorker</h1>
            <p class="lead"> Welcome to UpperWorker! <br> Do you need a handyman? Someone who takes care of your garden, the restoration of your old furniture or the painting of your house? <br> You need a special worker for your job; Perhaps a worker replacement for vacation, a babysitter for two hours, a craftsman or skilled worker, or you just want to share your work with others? Or maybe offer your help to people who really need it. <br> We want to share your experience, whether it's cutting roses, assembling boxes or screwing in a loose screw out there. Whatever your work here we value it, we want you to share your experience and take advantage of it. <br> Anywhere and anytime, someone may need your help.</p>
            <a href="/areas" class="btn button">
                <span>
                    Get Started!
                </span>
            </a>
        </main>

        <footer class="px-4 text-dark-50 pt-auto">
            <p>&copy; UpperWorker 2023</p>
        </footer>
    </div>




    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.7/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-zYPOMqeu1DAVkHiLqWBUTcbYfZ8osu1Nd6Z89ify25QV9guujx43ITvfi12/QExE" crossorigin="anonymous"></script> <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-Y4oOpwW3duJdCWv5ly8SCFYWqFDsfob/3GkgExXKV4idmbt98QcxXYs9UoXAB7BZ" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
